title: Unboxing: Bose SoundTouch 20 Series III Wireless Speaker
description:
Bose SoundTouch 20 Wireless Music System - www.abt.com

There’s a world of music out there. And the SoundTouch 20 wireless music system is a great way to play it throughout your home—wirelessly. It connects directly to your home Wi-Fi network so there’s no complicated equipment to worry about. You can even play your favorite music instantly. Simply press one of six presets on the speaker or remote and the music starts.
Place this compact system just about anywhere around your home and enjoy clear room-filling sound. The SoundTouch 20 system is part of an entire family of wireless speakers and systems for every room of your home. From one-piece music systems to outdoor speakers to home theater each one delivers the kind of audio quality you expect from Bose.
